* Table Update\nTriggers
** Supported Tables
***_ Delta & Iceberg managed tables
***_ External Delta tables
***_ Materialized views
***_ Streaming tables
***_ Views on supported tables
** Multiple Table Behavior
***_ Any table updated: run immediately
***_ All tables updated: wait for all
** Timing Options
***_ Min time between triggers
***_ Wait after last change (batching)
** Dynamic Parameters
***_ updated_tables list
***_ commit_timestamp
***_ table version number
** Tip
***_ Enable file events on external location
@endmindmap
